com.ning.billing.meter.timeline.chunks
Class TimelineChunk

java.lang.Object
  com.ning.billing.meter.timeline.chunks.TimelineChunk

public class TimelineChunk
extends Object

Instances of this class represent timeline sequences read from the database for a single source and single metric. The samples are held in a byte array.
